The paper discusses a method for improving document summarization using word embeddings, which is a common topic in natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) research. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. The use of word embeddings also suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence (AI), which could place the paper in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper's experimental evaluation and use of neural network techniques could also make it relevant to cs.DL (Deep Learning).
